raw_text = "~ start
## 11:34am
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Mabel: Ello
Mabel: Claaaass is finally over 😩
Player: Hey Mabes, how'd it go?
Mabel: I think my brain melted somewhere around the second lecture
Mabel: img: mabel/180
Mabel: Behold... your very fried agent 🫠😋🥰
- You look wiped out 😟
	Player: You look wiped out 😟
	Mabel: Is it that obvious 😭
- Rough day?
	Player: Rough day?
	Mabel: The roughest 🫡
Mabel: I look like I got run over by the sleep deprivation truck I knowww 😭
Mabel: Do I still look cute babe? 🥲
Player: Always
Mabel: 🥰
Mabel: It's all because of the noise from last night 🙄🙄
Player: The noisy neighbor?
Mabel: Yep!! He did NOT stop last night
Mabel: Like at all
Mabel: It went on basically till morning omg 😵‍💫
Mabel: Thought: There was definitely a girl in that room too
Player: Seriously? The whole night?
Mabel: The WHOLE night
Mabel: I got maybe two hours of sleep 😭
Mabel: Thought: Those sounds were so... strange
Mabel: Thought: What do you have to be doing to make sounds like that??
Mabel: My eyebags have eyebags now 🐼 I'm full panda now
Mabel: Would you still love me if I turned into a panda??
Player: Uh.. sure? 😅
Mabel: Excuse you, answer is \"YES!\" 😤
Player: YES!
Mabel: I'm just teasing you babe 😚
Mabel: But ugh..
Mabel: And I can't even nap yet 😣
Mabel: Gotta swing by the sorority house first 🥲
Player: Oh? What for?
Mabel: Honestly not totally sure 🤔
Mabel: Nina just said they need me for \"\"something\"\"
Mabel: Whatever that means lol
Mabel: I'll be quick and then SLEEEEP forever
Player: Lol okay, don't overdo it
Mabel: Never 🫡 I'm too tired for that anyway lol
Mabel: Okay wish me luck
Player: Good luck!!
do advance_time(3, 20)
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
set PhoneUnlocks.leak = \"nina3\"
Player: Hey Mabes, finished with the club stuff?
Mabel: Oh!!
Mabel: H-hi babe 😅
Mabel: Yep! Yes. All done. Totally fine 👍
Player: You ok? 😄
Mabel: Yes!! Why wouldn't I be hehe
Mabel: Thought: Am I seriously still sweating?
Mabel: Thought: Did they really need to give me all these??
Mabel: It just uh... wasn't really the kind of \"something\" I was picturing 😳
- What did they have you do?
	Player: What did they have you do?
	Mabel: Oh just, club stuff! 😅
	Mabel: They wanted a few pictures for my uhm... to set up my club social account
	Mabel: Thought: Quite a few...
	Player: That was all? 🤔
	Mabel: Yep! 
	Mabel: Guess it was no biggie huh, might just be tired then 😝 so dw
- You sure you're okay?
	Player: You sure you're okay?
	do echo_set([\"181\"])
	Mabel: Thought: Did I say something to give it away??
	Mabel: Thought: The last thing I want to do is worry babe...
	Mabel: I'm sure!! Promise 🥺
	Mabel: Just a loooong tiring day
Mabel: Thought: My face is still so red omg
Mabel: 😮‍💨
Mabel: Would it be okay if I went quiet tonight? 🥺
Mabel: I have SO much coursework piling up
Mabel: And I really really need to actually sleep afterward
Mabel: After last night I'm basically the walking dead
Player: Of course, get some rest
do echo_clear()
Mabel: Thank youuu!!
Mabel: You're seriously the best
Mabel: I'll be a functioning human again tomorrow I promise
Mabel: Thought: And maybe by then I'll have stopped thinking about that picture
Mabel: Good night Babe, thanks for worrying about me 🩷
Player: Night Mabes
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
